Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.65,0:00:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉近最喜欢与最讨厌的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.47,0:00:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二人的推理与悬疑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.40,0:00:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解读死亡讯息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.03,0:00:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文字和记号的奇妙联系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.05,0:00:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似小孩 智慧却过于常人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.63,0:00:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.21,0:01:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们几个和朱蒂老师一起来到咖啡馆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.43,0:01:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然整座大楼都停电了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.77,0:01:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在电力恢复后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:01:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡馆旁边的电梯上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.02,0:01:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现一具怀里抱着信封的尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.81,0:02:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被害人是信用调查社的社长中条胜则
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.00,0:02:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信封里面的资料被人拿走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.28,0:02:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信封表面用他的血写着○×△的讯息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.76,0:02:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部 血字找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.63,0:02:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,□
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以说是“口”这个字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是假名的“ロ”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据前面的○×△来看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是□
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加不明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个□比○×△稍微大一点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.12,0:02:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐藏匆忙中的省略（后篇）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 兰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,0:03:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.29,0:03:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,○×△合起来会不会是什么字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.82,0:03:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,□和×合起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就成了田字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.75,0:03:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 这个畭姓的人很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个姓很少见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过绳田这个姓有三个田呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 浅井的形状也很相近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形状
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.65,0:03:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啦 是形状啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.44,0:03:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说 铃木的铃因为是圆形的就用○表示
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.06,0:04:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也姓铃木啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姓铃木的没有坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 这里就交给我们警察来办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们赶快离开现场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.03,0:04:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.24,0:04:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里已经完事了 你去支援千叶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我去给爸爸打电话告诉他晚点回家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.19,0:04:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 是千叶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八层
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 警部让我上去支援你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 你等我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.47,0:05:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上上去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.20,0:05:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰小姐 有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.07,0:05:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X到底是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才不是说总有人恶作剧的给你写信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由美总是取笑我 发短信的时候总是写上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,×××
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不问早晚也会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.46,0:05:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 高木警官
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:06:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.03,0:06:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利可真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小家伙也不知道跑到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 cool kid的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.73,0:06:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.84,0:06:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.41,0:06:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,cool kid
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就是个鸵鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.52,0:06:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸵鸟…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么○×△□的意思你弄明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.57,0:06:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定正如毛利说的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.42,0:06:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在用形状表示什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.85,0:06:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说 美国国防部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫五角大楼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.85,0:06:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为大楼的形状是五角形的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以叫Pentagon
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.65,0:07:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在美国 有特殊含义的词汇非常非常多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,White House这个词本意是白色的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.64,0:07:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在代指总统府
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椭圆形办公室Ovail Office
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.37,0:07:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代指总统的办公室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有事务所bureau这个词
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个词
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,F.B.I
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.49,0:07:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是美国联邦调查局
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.37,0:07:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你有用吗 cool kid
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 刚才的鸵鸟是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是cool kid你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.97,0:07:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐藏在电梯下面的字却被你发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.03,0:07:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在美国 管这种人叫做鸵鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.75,0:07:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思维成熟得像个大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.76,0:07:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐藏在小小的身体里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就以为别人看不出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本也有这样的俗语
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏头不藏尾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏头不藏尾…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信封借我用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.87,0:08:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 犯人就在那31人之中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 立刻就叫人去调查
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.69,0:08:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长的电脑不要让人动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:08:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被害人是信用调查公司的社长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人犯很可能就是在他正在调查的贪污犯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我去问问他公司的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有人和他一起调查
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许知道贪污犯的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长独自在调查这件事 非常秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司职员都不知道这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他记录调查结果的电脑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.48,0:09:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是没有密码打不开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密码…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.45,0:09:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是密码啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个○×△□是不是密码呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.34,0:10:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也这么想才让人敲了○×△□试试
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.22,0:10:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是没有打开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是24种配列组合排列组合都试过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那○×△□果然还是犯人的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是个谜语吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本的猜谜节目
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是用这个符号表示Yes和No
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 ○×猜谜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.91,0:10:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么犯人是猜谜王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.50,0:10:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之你们在这里等着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.43,0:10:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再搅在案子里了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是如果○×△是犯人的名字的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.19,0:10:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千叶警官就有点嫌疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.49,0:10:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:10:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千叶警官的千字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遮住这边就是×
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.98,0:11:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遮住这边看上去就像△了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.77,0:11:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得非常可疑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.36,0:11:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遮…遮住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.92,0:11:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么想的话高木警官也很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.98,0:11:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 高木警官的高字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遮住这边既像□ 又像○
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.09,0:11:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像□我知道 怎么说像○呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.94,0:11:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为口这个字有人用○代替
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿笠博士写“阿”字也总是这么写
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士说匆忙的时候省略点也是应该的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.29,0:11:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐藏 匆忙 省略…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 千叶警官和高木警官是我报警之后才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们怎么会是犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.50,0:12:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听见了没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实这个嫌疑犯的清单上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.38,0:12:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实有…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.60,0:12:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.80,0:12:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得这个嫌疑犯的清单上确实有…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.97,0:12:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国吉文太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国吉文太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么○×△□说的是他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.32,0:12:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表面上看确实没有什么联系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把吉和文这两个字的上半部分遮住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.02,0:13:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 不是○×△吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 确实是○×△
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 把“太”这个字说成是△有点勉强吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,园子这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,印刷体确实不像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.17,0:13:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是手写体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且最后的点拖长点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.30,0:13:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 看上去很像△吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 为什么要遮住上半部分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是遮住的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被人拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.29,0:13:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写着○×△的是在信封的边上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来发现的□
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比○×△大一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就证明除了□以外的三个字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:14:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是跨在信封和露出来的资料上面的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.71,0:14:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 写着○×△上半部分的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被犯人拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那么□呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.04,0:14:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是国这个字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他必须要在犯人发现之前写下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国字就省略了中间的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 确实有这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餐具上光写外面一个框的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.99,0:14:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh Great
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直是从小说里走出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.87,0:14:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名侦探目暮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.88,0:14:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 找到嫌疑犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去楼上的公司
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.71,0:14:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 已经这么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利怎么还没回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能在给新一打电话问X的意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.70,0:15:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说得没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她知道了答案
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.19,0:15:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢 什么把我珍贵的X给人啊 园子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.70,0:15:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问了高木警官
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.76,0:15:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.12,0:15:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.37,0:15:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 要是新一跟我要X 我也没办法给他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.55,0:15:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不会知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.46,0:15:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他对这方面的知识很不敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.24,0:15:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 柯南去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.82,0:15:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不见了 那个小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会就不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.54,0:15:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国吉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.15,0:15:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 国吉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:15:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:16:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 有点事要问你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.14,0:16:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请跟我们来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.76,0:16:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎纸机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.76,0:16:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,□和○×△啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依靠推理找出不足的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我的名字国吉文太
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是警官先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.61,0:16:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光凭这个就断定我是犯人有点操之过急吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是被害人留下来的死亡讯息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可能是犯人用被害人的手写的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.35,0:16:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用血字嫁祸于我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.15,0:16:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果怀疑我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.76,0:17:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请找出那些被犯人拿走的资料再说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.81,0:17:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我是犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.15,0:17:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不会往杀人现场的这座楼里跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.97,0:17:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是逃到外面去 把资料销毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你把资料粉碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.62,0:17:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过因为那资料上有记号
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.44,0:17:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新粘起来比拼图还容易
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 高木警官
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.67,0:17:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.00,0:17:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 找到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只把沾有血迹的碎纸找出来拼上非常简单
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和信封上的血字完全吻合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.97,0:17:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些血字是国吉文太没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.27,0:17:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个能从碎纸机里找到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.45,0:17:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再花点时间 其它部分也可以找到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 另外
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人的手套被扔在回公司路上的厕所里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.56,0:18:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果国吉先生是用手将资料粉碎的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,资料上应该会有他的指纹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.92,0:18:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,○×△啊 原来是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.33,0:18:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.54,0:18:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大学时代的绰号 就叫做大口和○×△
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.57,0:18:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时我还不明白什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.64,0:18:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光是让孩子吃饱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也能让他们高兴高兴 所以开始贪污
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次成功了 从此贪污就成了习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.27,0:18:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小钱是无底洞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的欲望是无止境的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.48,0:18:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个○×△先生被抓住了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 现在正从后门带去警察局
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.40,0:19:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 能不能告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.03,0:19:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么想知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么想知道的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去问小兰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.49,0:19:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 她在那里发短信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…点…回…来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.89,0:19:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,园子姐姐让我问小兰姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.56,0:19:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,园子…不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.30,0:19:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.62,0:20:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 X是不行的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么毛利 铃木 回家路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到收获苹果的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.50,0:21:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没喝醉 还能喝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.49,0:21:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.93,0:22:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真吵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.89,0:22:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有短信来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.25,0:22:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是兰发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.75,0:22:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天又遇到案子了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.31,0:22:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.68,0:22:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然还是被诅咒了 我觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.60,0:22:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一喜欢听的案件内容以后再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.34,0:22:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.58,0:22:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,×××
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.88,0:22:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没戏 没戏 没戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.62,0:22:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能告诉我吗 Gin
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.65,0:22:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你相信有天堂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.41,0:22:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定会冷冷地回答
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.56,0:22:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“我不像你这样傻…”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.76,0:22:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请找到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.44,0:22:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们交杯共饮之前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.06,0:23:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有久藏的雪利酒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等不及了…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.62,0:23:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,×××
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.76,0:23:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well X 亲吻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.30,0:23:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅供女性表达她们的爱情…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.97,0:23:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也可以用做
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.46,0:23:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仇恨的标志…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.58,0:23:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.39,0:23:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X也同时意味着目标…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.26,0:23:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银质飞镖射中的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.30,0:23:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚出去 滚出去…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.49,0:23:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点从这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.75,0:24:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 什么闹鬼 真是白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.24,0:24:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还不是浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.14,0:24:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.53,0:24:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵屋的真相（前篇）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.39,0:24:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.63,0:24:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视画面
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.42,0:24:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集是春色浪漫的幽灵公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.08,0:24:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.11,0:24:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点恐怖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.01,0:24:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳗鱼怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:17.83,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop my love for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.93,0:00:27.60,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我俩讨论的未来中必定有你的归属
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.09,0:00:31.20,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh bady I can't stop my love for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.36,0:00:34.88,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意成为你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.48,0:00:43.04,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你我牵连的手发誓与你共此一生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.12,0:00:49.85,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“我讨厌你”这句话 即使是玩笑话我也不忍出口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.81,0:00:56.95,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“我喜欢你”如果不是事实我也不会说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.64,0:01:05.14,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你在无法见面时 没有心思顾及其他一般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.39,0:01:10.80,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心也被你一个人所独占
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:14.83,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop my love for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:24.44,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让我俩的爱分隔两地请你紧紧拥抱着我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.20,0:01:31.57,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此心绪不宁的夜晚仍会造访
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.52,0:01:39.55,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此时就请你给我一个大大的拥抱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:34.39,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每当清晨来临我便会想起你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:40.24,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时只要在你身边就感到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.87,0:20:47.05,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为恐惧时间的流逝黯然泪下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:52.07,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每每出现在不断改变的人心之中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.93,0:21:05.82,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不抱期待就不会失去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:12.66,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也别因此无欲无求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.90,0:21:20.05,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论前方是什么样的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.90,0:21:27.12,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在梦醒之后你的人依然在远方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:32.62,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我的心意先一步飘向你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.90,0:21:40.24,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落英缤纷的这条路依旧没有改变
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.50,0:21:45.84,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我依然想挽着你的手中漫步其中
